---
<BaseLayout
  title="Ecommerce Website Design Maryland | WooCommerce Experts"
  description="Ecommerce website design for Maryland businesses. WooCommerce with product schema, Stripe/PayPal checkout, 90+ PageSpeed. Fixed-scope from $1,500. Baltimore."
  canonicalUrl="https://upcomingbrand.com/industries/ecommerce-website-design/"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} slot="head" />
  <Navigation />

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="lfh-hero">

    <div class="container">
      <nav class="lfh-breadcrumb mono-xs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <a href="/#industries">Industries</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <span>WooCommerce Website Design</span>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="container lfh-wrap">

      <!-- LEFT COLUMN -->
      <div class="lfh-left">

        <div class="lfh-tags">
          <span class="lfh-pill">
            <span class="lfh-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            WooCommerce Store Design &middot; Maryland
          </span>
          <span class="lfh-hero-sep" aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
          <span class="lfh-hero-eyebrow">A specialist studio, not a template shop</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="lfh-h1">
          <span class="lfh-h1-line">Maryland WooCommerce stores</span>
          <span class="lfh-h1-line lfh-h1-accent-line"><em class="lfh-h1-accent">built to convert browsers</em></span>
          <span class="lfh-h1-line lfh-h1-italic">into buyers.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="lfh-lede">
          Maryland businesses need ecommerce website design that converts, not just a WooCommerce template. Most online stores leave money on the table: slow product pages, broken checkout flows on mobile, and no Product schema for search visibility. We build WooCommerce ecommerce websites for Maryland businesses that load fast, rank for product searches, and convert visitors into customers. Fixed-scope from <strong>$1,500</strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="lfh-ctas">
          <a href="#contact" class="lfh-btn-primary">
            Book a discovery call
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M1 7h12M8 2l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#pricing" class="lfh-btn-ghost">
            See pricing
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M2 12L12 2M12 2H5M12 2v7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="lfh-trust">
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="5.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-opacity="0.35"/><path d="M3.5 6l2 2 3-3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Maryland-based studio
          </span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">Product schema on every listing</span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">Fixed-scope &middot; no surprises</span>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT COLUMN - FORM -->
      <div class="lfh-right">
        <div class="lfh-form-card">
          <div class="lfh-form-header">
            <p class="lfh-form-eyebrow">Free store audit</p>
            <h2 class="lfh-form-title">Is your store losing sales?</h2>
            <p class="lfh-form-sub">We review your current store and send a plain-English audit within 2 business days. No sales call required.</p>
          </div>

          <form class="lfh-form" name="ec-inquiry" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" data-netlify="true" action="/thank-you/">
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="ec-inquiry" />
            <div style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;width:1px;height:1px;overflow:hidden;" aria-hidden="true">
              <label>Leave blank: <input type="text" name="bot-field" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" /></label>
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <label class="lfh-form-label" for="ec-name">Your name</label>
              <input class="lfh-form-input" type="text" id="ec-name" name="name" placeholder="Dana Holloway" required autocomplete="name" />
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <label class="lfh-form-label" for="ec-email">Email address</label>
              <input class="lfh-form-input" type="email" id="ec-email" name="email" placeholder="dana@chesapeakegoods.com" required autocomplete="email" />
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <label class="lfh-form-label" for="ec-store">Store name</label>
              <input class="lfh-form-input" type="text" id="ec-store" name="store" placeholder="Chesapeake Goods Co." autocomplete="organization" />
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <span class="lfh-form-label" id="lbl-store-type">Store type</span>
              <div class="lf-cs-wrap" role="combobox" aria-expanded="false" aria-labelledby="lbl-store-type" data-name="store_type">
                <button type="button" class="lf-cs-trigger" aria-haspopup="listbox">
                  <span class="lf-cs-val">Select store type</span>
                  <svg class="lf-cs-chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 4l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                </button>
                <ul class="lf-cs-list" role="listbox" aria-label="Store type">
                  <li class="lf-cs-opt" role="option" data-value="Physical Products">Physical Products</li>
                  <li class="lf-cs-opt" role="option" data-value="Digital Downloads">Digital Downloads</li>
                  <li class="lf-cs-opt" role="option" data-value="Subscriptions">Subscriptions</li>
                  <li class="lf-cs-opt" role="option" data-value="Handmade / Artisan">Handmade / Artisan</li>
                  <li class="lf-cs-opt" role="option" data-value="Wholesale / B2B">Wholesale / B2B</li>
                  <li class="lf-cs-opt" role="option" data-value="Local Pickup + Shipping">Local Pickup + Shipping</li>
                  <li class="lf-cs-opt" role="option" data-value="Service + Products">Service + Products</li>
